<pb facs="1079396" n="1"/>
<opener><salute>
<lb/>Sapientissimo ac Celeberrimo Viro
             <lb/><choice><abbr>Jo:</abbr><expan>Johanni</expan></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Bernoull<choice><orig><g ref="#j">j</g></orig><reg>i</reg></choice></rs>
             Petrus Antonius <rs key="pers_DE-588-102552517" type="person">Michelottus</rs> <abbr>S. P. D.</abbr></salute></opener>
<p>Quum vehementer <rs key="B_1723-05-01_991170515108405501" type="letter">literas tuas</rs><note type="editorial">Johann I Bernoulli an Pietro Antonio Michelotti, vom 1. Mai 1723.</note>, Vir Amicissime, exspec<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>tarem quotidie, aliquando mihi tradit<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> sunt <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice>
             <lb/>Filio tuo <rs key="pers_DE-588-118656503" type="person">Daniele</rs> summi ingenii, magn<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>que
             <lb/>exspectationis adolescente, post calendas
             <lb/>majas. Ex quibus Te sanum esse, beneque
             <lb/>valere maximo cum gaudio intellexi. Sua<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>vissimum, ac eruditissimum <rs key="pers_DE-588-118656503" type="person">Filium</rs> tuum modo
             <lb/>commemoratum inexplicabili voluptate
             <lb/>complexus sum, rogavi<choice><orig><g ref="#que">U+E8BF</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> ut apud me com<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>morari vellet studiorum medico-practicor<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>,
             <lb/>nec non tuend<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> valetudinis causa. Sed quoniam
             <lb/>Nobilissimi Comitis <rs key="pers_DE-588-121710742" type="person">Vezzi</rs> Lares inhabitare ipsi
             <lb/>placet, rogare destiti, cohortatus tamen
             <lb/>sum ut quamprimum fieri poterit, quotidie
             <lb/>horis pomeridianis ad me se conferat, me<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>cumque domo exiens ad meos <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>gros
             <lb/>videndos, ad morborum consuetudines obser<pb facs="1079397" n="2"/>vandas, nec non ad medicamentor<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> operationes perpen<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>dendas multum studii adhibere velit. Se id pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>stitu<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>rum pollicitus est statim ac <choice><orig><g ref="#egrav">è</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice> rure in Urbem<!-- orttag -->
<lb/>redibit, etenim <hi rend="#u"><rs key="place_GEO-3172301" type="place">Nervesam</rs></hi> petiit una cum <choice><abbr>Ill<hi rend="#sup">mo</hi></abbr><expan>Illustrissimo</expan></choice><note type="editorial">Tatsächlichen Buchstabenbestand nochmals prüfen.</note>
<lb/>et <choice><abbr>Excell.<hi rend="#sup">o</hi></abbr><expan>Excellentissimo</expan></choice> <choice><abbr>D.</abbr><expan>Domino</expan></choice> <choice><abbr>Jo:</abbr><expan>Johanne</expan></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-121710742" type="person">Vezzi</rs> triduum ante, dixit<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>que se huc rediturum sub huius mensis finem.
             <lb/>De illius salute <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>que ac de mea (quod Tibi sanc<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>te polliceor) sollicitus ero. Ictero flavo aliquot
             <lb/>dies <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>grotavit, at remedio rhabarbari pulve<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>rati, et optim<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> Di<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>t<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> auxilio, me authore
             <lb/>convaluit. Cum ad Te scribet hortare etiam
             <lb/>atque etiam ut c<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>teris posthabitis rebus medi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>cin<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> practic<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> mecum operam dare omnibus
             <lb/>viribus allaboret: ipsi enim vel apud
             <lb/>nobilissimos utriusque sex<choice><orig><g ref="#uhat">û</g></orig><reg>u</reg></choice>s <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>grotantes facilem accessum procurabo
             <lb/>uti hactenus me fecisse, ex eo scivisse Te
             <lb/>nequaquam dubito. Vide igitur, Illus<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>trissime Vir, quantum commendatio Tua
             <lb/>apud me possit, quantamque vim in pos<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>terum habitura sit. Ipsum pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>stantissi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>mum <rs key="pers_DE-588-118656503" type="person">Filium</rs> mei filii loco habiturum,
             <lb/>eique omnem meam operam in omnibus rebus
             <lb/>honestis me pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>stiturum etiam atque etiam spondeo.
             <pb facs="1079398" n="3"/>
<lb/>Gratias habeo maximas pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ograv">ò</g></orig><reg>o</reg></choice> iis qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> ad me rescripsis<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>ti super ea, quam Tibi proposui difficul<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>tate spectante ad quantitatem aqu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> per
             <lb/>foramen in fundo vasis factum dato tempore
             <lb/>exilientis. Si <rs key="pers_DE-588-116692782" type="person">Helvetii</rs> Viri Clarissimi <rs key="biblio_52ARVVGE" type="biblio">schediasma</rs>
<lb/><choice><abbr>Comment.</abbr><expan>Commentarii</expan></choice> <choice><abbr>Reg.</abbr><expan>Regiae</expan></choice> <choice><abbr>Acad.</abbr><expan>Academiae</expan></choice> <choice><abbr>Scient.</abbr><expan>Scientiarum</expan></choice> <choice><abbr>Paris.</abbr><expan>Parisii</expan></choice> <choice><abbr>An.</abbr><expan>Anni</expan></choice> 1718 pag. 222
             <lb/>insertum<note type="editorial">Steht über "legere". Normalerweise ergänzt Michelotti unterhalb der Zeile. Stimmt die einsetzung vor "legere"</note> legere per otium aliquando Tibi liceret, rogare aude<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>rem ut attente perpenderes qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> ille de vi aëris
             <lb/>ad condensandum sanguin<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> ven<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> pulmonaris
             <lb/>ramulos, ac ramos pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>terfluent<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> protulit, rescri<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>beresque quid Tibi de <rs key="pers_DE-588-116692782" type="person">Helvetianis</rs>
<lb/>ratiocinationibus videretur. De hac
             <lb/>eadem re acutissim<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> Filium tuum <rs key="pers_DE-588-118656503" type="person">Da<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>nielem</rs> rogavi, interim meas ad
             <lb/>illud ipsum schediasma paravi
             <lb/>Animadversiones, non enim mihi
             <lb/>videtur absolute verum esse san<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>guin<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> ab aëre inspirato cogi in
             <lb/>pulmone, pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>tereaque improba<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>bile videtur sanguinem confertiorem esse in
             <lb/>arteriis omnibus quam in venis. Cogita qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>so, at<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>que perpende cur ven<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> in corpore humano, omni<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>busque animantibus ampliores fact<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> sint qu<choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice>m
             <lb/><choice><sic>aerteri<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></sic><corr>arteri<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></corr></choice>, cur dexter cordis ventriculus amplior sinis<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>tro, dextra auricula sinistr<choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">â</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> capacior, uti et ar<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>teria pulmonaris vena pulmonari capacior
             <lb/>constituta <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> natura fuerit. Si quid de his om<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>nibus rebus sentias ad me quam citissime scripseris
             <lb/>majorem in modum me Tibi devinxeris.</p> <closer><salute>Vale Vir Celeberrime,
                <lb/>mihique, quod facis, favere perge.</salute> <dateline><choice><abbr>D.</abbr><expan>Dabam</expan></choice> raptim <rs key="place_GEO-3164603" type="place">Venetiis</rs> <choice><abbr>a. d.</abbr><expan>ad diem</expan></choice> <date when="1723-06-04">4 Junii 1723</date></dateline>
<pb facs="1079399" n="4"/>
<address>
<addrLine>A Monsieur</addrLine>
<addrLine>Monsieur Jean Bernoull<choice><orig><g ref="#j">j</g></orig><reg>i</reg></choice></addrLine>
<addrLine>Professeur tres celebre de</addrLine>
<addrLine>Matematique</addrLine>
<addrLine>franca per <rs key="place_GEO-2775220" type="place">Insprug</rs>à <rs key="place_GEO-2661604" type="place">Basle</rs></addrLine>
